            "text": "[![LegislationCrest](/images/crests/ukpga.gif)](/ukpga/2007/9/introduction/enacted?view=plain)",
            "tokenCum": 43,
            "children": [
                {
                    "type": "Heading",
                    "prefix": "#",
                    "text": "Rating (Empty Properties) Act 2007",
                    "tokenCum": 55,
                    "wordSum": 5,
                    "tokenSum": 13,
                    "tokenCount": 12
                },
                {
                    "type": "Heading",
                    "prefix": "#",
                    "text": "2007 CHAPTER 9",
                    "tokenCum": 63,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "Text",
                            "prefix": "",
                            "text": "An Act to make provision for and in connection with the liability of owners ofunoccupied hereditaments to a non-domestic rate.",
                            "tokenCum": 94,
                            "wordSum": 20,
                            "tokenSum": 32,
                            "tokenCount": 32
                        }
                    ],
                    "wordSum": 23,
                    "tokenSum": 41,
                    "tokenCount": 8
                },
                {
                    "type": "Text",
                    "prefix": "",
                    "text": "[19th July 2007]",
                    "tokenCum": 105,
                    "wordSum": 3,
                    "tokenSum": 12,
                    "tokenCount": 11
                },
                {
                    "type": "Text",
                    "prefix": "",
                    "text": "Most Gracious Sovereign,",
                    "tokenCum": 112,
                    "wordSum": 3,
                    "tokenSum": 8,
                    "tokenCount": 7
                },
                {
                    "type": "Text",
                    "prefix": "",
                    "text": "We, Your Majesty\u2019s most dutiful and loyal subjects, the Commons of the UnitedKingdom in Parliament assembled, towards making an addition to the publicrevenue, have freely and voluntarily resolved to give and grant unto YourMajesty the increases in non-domestic rating receipts resulting from theprovisions hereinafter made; and do therefore most humbly beseech Your Majestythat it may be enacted, and be it enacted, by the Queen\u2019s most ExcellentMajesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Lords Spiritual andTemporal, and Commons, in this present Parliament assembled, and by theauthority of the same, as follows:\u2014",
                    "tokenCum": 268,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 1",
                            "text": "Unoccupied hereditaments: chargeable amount",
                            "tokenCum": 278,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "In section 45 of the Local Government Finance Act [1988 (c.41)](/id/ukpga/1988/41?view=plain \"Go to item of legislation\") (unoccupiedhereditaments: liability), for subsection (4) (determination of chargeableamount) substitute\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 355,
                                    "wordSum": 25,
                                    "tokenSum": 79,
                                    "tokenCount": 79
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "\u201c(4)",
                                    "text": "Subject to subsection (4A) and to section 45A below, the chargeable amountfor a chargeable day shall be calculated in accordance with the formula\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 392,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Text",
                                            "prefix": "",
                                            "text": "[![](/ukpga/2007/9/images/ukpga_20070009_en_001)](/ukpga/2007/9/images/ukpga_20070009_en_001?view=plain)",
                                            "tokenCum": 464,
                                            "wordSum": 1,
                                            "tokenSum": 75,
                                            "tokenCount": 75
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 24,
                                    "tokenSum": 114,
                                    "tokenCount": 38
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "where A, B and C have the meanings given by section 46.",
                                    "tokenCum": 481,
                                    "wordSum": 12,
                                    "tokenSum": 19,
                                    "tokenCount": 19
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "(4A)An order may provide that subsection (4) shall have effect as if thefollowing formula were substituted\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 509,
                                    "wordSum": 16,
                                    "tokenSum": 30,
                                    "tokenCount": 30
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "[![](/ukpga/2007/9/images/ukpga_20070009_en_002)](/ukpga/2007/9/images/ukpga_20070009_en_002?view=plain)",
                                    "tokenCum": 581,
                                    "wordSum": 1,
                                    "tokenSum": 74,
                                    "tokenCount": 74
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "where N is such number (greater than one but not greater than two) as may beprescribed.",
                                    "tokenCum": 603,
                                    "wordSum": 16,
                                    "tokenSum": 24,
                                    "tokenCount": 24
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Text",
                                    "prefix": "",
                                    "text": "(4B)An order under subsection (4A) may be made\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 620,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(a)",
                                            "text": "in relation to England, by the Secretary of State;",
                                            "tokenCum": 631,
                                            "wordSum": 9,
                                            "tokenSum": 14,
                                            "tokenCount": 14
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(b)",
                                            "text": "in relation to Wales, by the Welsh Ministers.\u201d.",
                                            "tokenCum": 644,
                                            "wordSum": 8,
                                            "tokenSum": 16,
                                            "tokenCount": 16
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 25,
                                    "tokenSum": 49,
                                    "tokenCount": 18
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "After that section insert\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 649,
                                    "wordSum": 4,
                                    "tokenSum": 7,
                                    "tokenCount": 7
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Heading",
                                    "prefix": "###",
                                    "text": "\u201c45AUnoccupied hereditaments: zero-rating",
                                    "tokenCum": 663,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Digit point",
                                            "prefix": "(1)",
                                            "text": "Where section 45 applies in relation to a hereditament, the chargeableamount for a chargeable day is zero in the following cases.",
                                            "tokenCum": 693,
                                            "wordSum": 21,
                                            "tokenSum": 33,
                                            "tokenCount": 33
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Digit point",
                                            "prefix": "(2)",
                                            "text": "The first case is where\u2014",
                                            "tokenCum": 699,
                                            "children": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(a)",
                                                    "text": "the ratepayer is a charity or trustees for a charity, and",
                                                    "tokenCum": 716,
                                                    "wordSum": 11,
                                                    "tokenSum": 21,
                                                    "tokenCount": 21
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(b)",
                                                    "text": "it appears that when next in use the hereditament will be wholly or mainlyused for charitable purposes (whether of that charity or of that and othercharities).",
                                                    "tokenCum": 753,
                                                    "wordSum": 26,
                                                    "tokenSum": 41,
                                                    "tokenCount": 41
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "wordSum": 42,
                                            "tokenSum": 71,
                                            "tokenCount": 8
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Digit point",
                                            "prefix": "(3)",
                                            "text": "The second case is where\u2014",
                                            "tokenCum": 759,
                                            "children": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(a)",
                                                    "text": "the ratepayer is a registered club for the purposes of Schedule 18 to theFinance Act 2002 (community amateur sports clubs), and",
                                                    "tokenCum": 793,
                                                    "wordSum": 21,
                                                    "tokenSum": 38,
                                                    "tokenCount": 38
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(b)",
                                                    "text": "it appears that when the hereditament is next in use\u2014",
                                                    "tokenCum": 806,
                                                    "wordSum": 10,
                                                    "tokenSum": 17,
                                                    "tokenCount": 17
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(i)",
                                                    "text": "it will be wholly or mainly used for the purposes of that club and thatclub will be such a registered club, or",
                                                    "tokenCum": 831,
                                                    "wordSum": 22,
                                                    "tokenSum": 29,
                                                    "tokenCount": 29
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(ii)",
                                                    "text": "it will be wholly or mainly used for the purposes of two or more clubsincluding that club, and each of those clubs will be such a registered club.\u201d.",
                                                    "tokenCum": 865,
                                                    "wordSum": 28,
                                                    "tokenSum": 38,
                                                    "tokenCount": 38
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "wordSum": 86,
                                            "tokenSum": 131,
                                            "tokenCount": 8
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Digit point",
                                            "prefix": "(3)",
                                            "text": "In section 143 of that Act (orders and regulations), after subsection (3A)insert\u2014",
                                            "tokenCum": 889,
                                            "children": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Text",
                                                    "prefix": "",
                                                    "text": "\u201c(3B)The power to make an order under section 45(4A) shall be exercisable bystatutory instrument, and no such order shall be made\u2014",
                                                    "tokenCum": 928,
                                                    "wordSum": 21,
                                                    "tokenSum": 43,
                                                    "tokenCount": 43
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(a)",
                                                    "text": "in the case of an order relating to England, unless a draft of the orderhas been laid before and approved by resolution of each House of Parliament;",
                                                    "tokenCum": 959,
                                                    "wordSum": 27,
                                                    "tokenSum": 35,
                                                    "tokenCount": 35
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "Alpha point",
                                                    "prefix": "(b)",
                                                    "text": "in the case of an order relating to Wales, unless a draft of the order hasbeen laid before and approved by resolution of the National Assembly forWales.\u201d.",
                                                    "tokenCum": 994,
                                                    "wordSum": 27,
                                                    "tokenSum": 39,
                                                    "tokenCount": 39
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "wordSum": 87,
                                            "tokenSum": 144,
                                            "tokenCount": 26
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 239,
                                    "tokenSum": 395,
                                    "tokenCount": 15
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 366,
                            "tokenSum": 802,
                            "tokenCount": 10
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 2",
                            "text": "Consequential provisions",
                            "tokenCum": 999,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "Schedule 1 provides for consequential amendments.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1011,
                                    "wordSum": 6,
                                    "tokenSum": 14,
                                    "tokenCount": 14
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "The enactments specified in Schedule 2 are repealed.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1025,
                                    "wordSum": 8,
                                    "tokenSum": 16,
                                    "tokenCount": 16
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 16,
                            "tokenSum": 36,
                            "tokenCount": 5
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "Heading",
                            "prefix": "## 3",
                            "text": "Short title, commencement and extent",
                            "tokenCum": 1033,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(1)",
                                    "text": "The short title of this Act is the Rating (Empty Properties) Act 2007.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1054,
                                    "wordSum": 13,
                                    "tokenSum": 23,
                                    "tokenCount": 23
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(2)",
                                    "text": "The provisions of this Act come into force on the day this Act is passed.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1071,
                                    "wordSum": 15,
                                    "tokenSum": 19,
                                    "tokenCount": 19
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(3)",
                                    "text": "The provisions of this Act have effect in relation to the year 2008-09 andsubsequent financial years.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1099,
                                    "wordSum": 16,
                                    "tokenSum": 30,
                                    "tokenCount": 30
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(4)",
                                    "text": "Any provision of this Act relating to the making of regulations or ordershas effect as from the passing of this Act as regards the making of provisionin relation to any such year.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1136,
                                    "wordSum": 32,
                                    "tokenSum": 39,
                                    "tokenCount": 39
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(5)",
                                    "text": "If the power to make regulations by virtue of paragraph 4 of Schedule 1(change of state of property to be disregarded) is exercised before 1st April2008, it may be exercised so that the regulations\u2014",
                                    "tokenCum": 1190,
                                    "children": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(a)",
                                            "text": "apply to acts or omissions taking place at any time after the regulationscome into force, and",
                                            "tokenCum": 1210,
                                            "wordSum": 16,
                                            "tokenSum": 23,
                                            "tokenCount": 23
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "Alpha point",
                                            "prefix": "(b)",
                                            "text": "also have effect in relation to the year 2007-08.",
                                            "tokenCum": 1227,
                                            "wordSum": 9,
                                            "tokenSum": 20,
                                            "tokenCount": 20
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "wordSum": 59,
                                    "tokenSum": 99,
                                    "tokenCount": 55
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "Digit point",
                                    "prefix": "(6)",
                                    "text": "This Act extends to England and Wales.",
                                    "tokenCum": 1235,
                                    "wordSum": 7,
                                    "tokenSum": 10,
                                    "tokenCount": 10
                                }
                            ],
                            "wordSum": 147,
                            "tokenSum": 229,
                            "tokenCount": 8
                        }
                    ],
                    "wordSum": 622,
                    "tokenSum": 1224,
                    "tokenCount": 156
                }
            ],
